                "type": "link"
              },
              "name": "Player Core",
              "page": 453,
              "type": "source"
            }
          ],
          "text": "A creature similar to an animal but with an Intelligence modifier of \u20133 or higher is usually a beast. Unlike an animal, a beast might be able to speak and reason.",
